# AgentGate live-provider proof setup
#
# This file is only for local testing. It is gitignored.
# Most users can leave this file mostly blank if Codex and/or Claude Code
# already work on this machine.
#
# Then run:
#   pnpm live:openai
#   pnpm live:anthropic
#   pnpm live:mcp
#   pnpm live:matrix
#
# OpenAI note:
# OpenAI live proof can use either:
# 1) a logged-in Codex session (`codex login`) for the subscription-style tandem path, or
# 2) OPENAI_API_KEY for the lower-level Responses API path.
OPENAI_API_KEY=
# Optional advanced override for the raw OpenAI API path only.
# Most users should leave this unset.
# OPENAI_MODEL=

# Anthropic note:
# Anthropic live proof can use either:
# 1) ANTHROPIC_API_KEY for the SDK path, or
# 2) a logged-in Claude Code session (`claude auth login` or `claude setup-token`)
#    for the Claude Code tandem path.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# Optional advanced override for the raw Anthropic SDK path only.
# Most users should leave this unset.
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=
